name: Super Impostor Bros.
overview: SUPER IMPOSTOR BROS. is an Among Us fangame made for the GameBoy Color. Part platformer, part visual novel, play it in your web browser, or download the rom and play it on an emulator or an actual GameBoy Color! This is a free fan game, not affiliated with Innersloth. Support them by purchasing Among Us! Each stage has 5 hidden ID cards. Collect all 5 in a stage to unlock a special item. The special item gives you a different choice in the cutscenes at the end of the level. There is also a hidden room in each of the 3 stages. Can you find them all?
